    <briefdescription>
<para>A reference counting wrapper for a vector class that allows a set of referencing smart pointers to collaborate in managing its lifetime and eventually cleaning it up. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This should only be allocated on the new/delete heap, not a thread&apos;s stack. <parameterlist kind="templateparam"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>T</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>type of the data that the vector holds </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
